#'     The columns are `Monocytes`, `Unknown`, `CD4Tcells`, `Bcells`, `NK`,
#'     and `CD8Tcells`.
#'   }
#'   \item{bulk_expression_profiles}{
#'     A numeric matrix or data frame with 35,688 features and 20 bulk PBMC
#'     samples.
#'   }
#'   \item{probe_ids}{
#'     Probe identifiers corresponding to the rows of
#'     `bulk_expression_profiles`.
#'   }
#' }
#'
#' Ground-truth cell type proportions are available for the following cell
#' types:
#'
#' \describe{
#'   \item{Monocytes}{Monocytes}
#'   \item{Unknown}{Unassigned or remaining cell type fraction}
#'   \item{CD4Tcells}{CD4 T cells}
#'   \item{Bcells}{B cells}
#'   \item{NK}{Natural killer cells}
#'   \item{CD8Tcells}{CD8 T cells}
#' }
#'
#' The data included here were processed and reformatted by Sergej Ruff for use
#' with QUASAR deconvolution workflows. No endorsement by the original data
#' providers is implied.
#'
#' @format A named list with three elements:
#' \describe{
#'   \item{ground_truth_proportions}{
#'     A 20 x 6 matrix or data frame containing ground-truth PBMC cell type
#'     proportions.
#'   }
#'   \item{bulk_expression_profiles}{
#'     A 35,688 x 20 matrix or data frame containing bulk expression profiles.
#'   }
#'   \item{probe_ids}{
#'     A vector of probe identifiers corresponding to the expression profile
#'     rows.
#'   }
#' }
#'
#' @source
#' Gene Expression Omnibus accession GSE65133:
#' \url{https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/geo/query/acc.cgi?acc=GSE65133}
#'
#' Newman AM, Liu CL, Green MR, Gentles AJ, Feng W, Xu Y, Hoang CD,
#' Diehn M, Alizadeh AA, Maecker H, Davis MM. Robust enumeration of cell
#' subsets from tissue expression profiles. Nature Methods. 2015;12(5):453-457.
